channel.title: Need help with woodcutting
channel.description:
Hi, A Short while ago i added some woodcutting to my server.. The first time i just got logs from trees.. I edited that to 5k from normal tree but now all trees give 5k.. Does someone know how to edit that? (i want other trees to give another amounts)
Greetings, Forca

item.title: Need help with woodcutting
item.dc:creator: @I_Forca_I I Forca I
item.description:
@I_Forca_I wrote:

[quote=“Zanzibar, post:2, topic:104770”]Thats For The Reg. Tree.

case 1276: if(actionTimer == 0) { sendMessage("Zanzibar Rules!!"); addSkillXP((1000*playerLevel[8]), 8); addItem(ITEM ID, ITEM AMOUNT); setAnimation(4); updateRequired = true; appearanceUpdateRequired = true; }
Meh I Dunno If Thats Right…

For The Other Trees Copy That And Change The 1276 To The Other Tree ID #[/quote]
Lol and i change the Message (h)

But Thanks mate
